The files of this projects are from various sources on the internet,
especially Mike Kazantsev post

http://blog.fraggod.net/2015/03/28/bluetooth-pan-network-setup-with-bluez-5x.html

Modifications to enable automatic authentication are from
Merlin Schumacher <mls@ct.de> from c't Magazin (www.ct.de).

Both scripts base on sample bluetooth scripts provided with bluez.
